The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 6™ April, 2008 :-
Shri Vayalar Ravi assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
Parliamentary Affairs. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of
the Minister of Overseas Indian Affairs;
i)

Minister of Parliamentary Affairs. He will continue to hold the charge of
the office of the Minister of Information and Broadcasting;
ii)

Minister of Youth Affairs and Sports. He will continue to hold the charge
of the office of the Minister of Panchayati Raj and the Minister of
Development of North Eastern Region;

(Independent charge) of the Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports;
